      "date": "2001-06-01T04:44:00-07:00",
      "body": "TECO Ben, I made a minor adjustment to the LOI re: exclusivity. Policy states that any time we sign up to exclusivity we are supposed to get it approved by Mark Metts, Tim Detmering and the CEO of the affected business unit. Seems a little silly in this case, but it can't hurt. (yes, I know we didn't do it with the turbine stuff) Kay "
